Joy Brook https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joy_Brook 0 Joy Brook (born Joy Beadle, 9 May 1969 in Scarborough, North Riding of Yorkshire) is an English actress who played DC Kerry Holmes in The Bill and Joanne Pearson in Peak Practice. She has also appeared in The Thin Blue Line, Dalziel and Pascoe, Dream Team and Doctors. She can currently be seen in the short Maltesers sponsor films that accompany Loose Women on ITV1. She can currently be seen in the short Go Compare adverts on TV, and appeared as Dr. Melville in Emmerdale on 12 January 2018 Joy_Brook ( born Joy_Beadle , 9_May_1969 in Scarborough , North_Riding of Yorkshire ) is an_English_actress who played DC_Kerry_Holmes in The_Bill_and_Joanne_Pearson in Peak_Practice .
